r=[[BBC]] | work=BBC Sport | date=27 August 2013 | accessdate=19 April 2020}}</ref> and the fourth round of the [[2013\u201314 Scottish Cup|Scottish Cup]], losing to [[Dundee United F.C.|Dundee United]].<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/football/25063966 | title=Dundee United 5-2 Kilmarnock | publisher=[[BBC]] | work=BBC Sport | date=29 November 2013 | accessdate=19 April 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Results & fixtures==\n{{legend2|#ccffcc|Win|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend2|#ffffcc|Draw|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend2|#ffcccc|Loss|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n{{legend2|#cccccc|Postponed|border=1px solid #AAAAAA}}\n\n===Pre season===\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|result  = W\n|nobars =  1\n|date = 17 July 2013\n|time = 19:45\n|round = [[Friendly match|Friendly]]\n|score = 0 \u2013 1 \n|report = [https://archive.is/20130730113617/http://www.kilmarnockfc.co.uk/articles/20130718/east-fife-0-1-kilmarnock_85961_3307614 Report]\n|team1 = [[East Fife F.C.|East Fife]]\n|team2 = [[Kilmarnock F.C.|Kilmarnock]]\n|goals1 = \n|goals2 = Trialist {{goal|1}}\n|stadium =[[Bayview Stadium]], [[Methil]]\n|attendance = \n|referee =\n|motm =\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|result  = W\n|nobars =  1\n|date = 20 July 2013\n|time = 14:00\n|round = [[Friendly match|Friendly]]\n|score = 0 \u2013 2 \n|report = [http://www.scotsman.com/sport/football/spfl/kilmarnock-2-2-carlisle-united-killie-bag-draw-1-3017953 Report]\n|team1 = [[Glentoran F.C.|Glentoran]]\n|team2 = [[Kilmarnock F.C.|Kilmarnock]]\n|goals1 = \n|goals2 = [[Paul Heffernan|Heffernan]] {{goal| pen}}{{goal|}}\n|stadium =[[The Oval (Belfast)|The Oval]], [[Belfast]]\n|attendance = \n|referee =\n|motm =\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|result  = D\n|nobars =  1\n|date = 26 July 2013\n|time = 19:45\n|round = [[Friendly match|Friendly]]\n|score = 2 \u2013 2 \n|report = [http://www.scotsman.com/sport/football/spfl/kilmarnock-2-2-carlisle-united-killie-bag-draw-1-3017953 Report]\n|team1 = [[Kilmarnock F.C.|Kilmarnock]]\n|t